# Research: Phishing Attacks

## What is Phishing?
Phishing is when attackers pretend to be legitimate organizations to steal sensitive information.

## Common Types
- Email phishing
- Spear phishing (targeted attacks)
- Smishing (SMS phishing)
- Vishing (voice call phishing)

## Prevention Methods
- Employee training
- Email filtering
- Multi-factor authentication
- Regular security updates
